## Completed Work This Session

### Project: vigil — All 5 phases (Tasks #706-710)
Drop-in Go replacement for mitchellh/go-ps. Cross-platform process listing with Process struct (PID, PPID, Executable, Path, Args, User). List, Find, Children, Iter (iter.Seq2) with context support. Platform implementations: Linux (/proc), macOS (sysctl+proc_pidpath+KERN_PROCARGS2), Windows (CreateToolhelp32Snapshot+QueryFullProcessImageName+OpenProcessToken), FreeBSD (sysctl+/proc), Solaris (/proc/psinfo). Compat layer (vigil/compat) matching go-ps Process interface. Go 1.23+, zero deps. 88.8% test coverage with 22 tests + 3 benchmarks. CI green on Go 1.23-1.24.

